## Database
- **Engine**: sqflite (mobile) + sqflite_common_ffi (desktop)
- **Schema version**: 50
- **Tables**: 35 (core 5, entries 3, contractors 2, personnel 2, quantities 2, photos 1, documents 1, toolbox 4, exports 2, consent 1, support 1, sync 8, extraction 2)
- **Supabase**: 53 migrations, 1 edge function (`daily-sync-push`), Postgres 17, Realtime enabled

